headline: Dow Jones Industrial Average's top-performing stocks of 2025
summary: Ahead of the new year, Yahoo Finance Markets and Data Editor Jared Blikre takes a closer look at some of the Dow Jones Industrial Average's (^DJI) best performers in 2025: Caterpillar (CAT), Goldman Sachs (GS), Johnson & Johnson (JNJ), and IBM (IBM). To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Morning Brief.

headline: 3 Volatile Stocks with Open Questions
summary: Market swings can be tough to stomach, and volatile stocks often experience exaggerated moves in both directions. While many thrive during risk-on environments, many also struggle to maintain investor confidence when the ride gets bumpy.
